  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>Hotel Sunstar is provided on a bed and breakfast board basis with the option to upgrade to half board.</p>
<p>Breakfast is served in the <span>Ambiance Restaurant. You can start your day at the buffet including a variety of cereals, muesli, fresh fruit, breads, regional cheeses and meats, </span></p>
<p>If you have upgraded to half board, you can enjoy a four course buffet style evening meal with choice of dishes in the Ambiance Restaurant.</p>
<p>The hotel also has a Swiss speciality a la carte restaurant - the Adlerstube, which serves fresh and sustainable products from the region. Warm up with a fondue with cheese from Grindelwald and fresh bread from the bakery or try their speciality tomahawk steak. Additional fees apply for dining in the Adlerstube.</p>
<p>A Christmas and New Year gala dinners is included.</p>
<p>Free selection of soft drinks in the minibar (alternatives extra).</p>
<p> </p>]]></cateringDescription>
