  <locationDescription><![CDATA[<p>Hotel Sunstar is located directly opposite the gondola for Grindelwald's own 'First' ski area.</p>
<p>The hotel enjoys an ideal location for the skiing and is close to the resort's après-ski and nightlife.</p>
<p>It is a 3 minutes' walk (300 metres) from the village centre and the resort bus stops is just outside the hotel building.</p>
<p><strong>Swiss Short Breaks</strong> available from 3 nights upwards</p>]]></locationDescription>
