  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Standard Nova Twin Rooms </strong>are around 20-22m² and sleep up to two. These rooms have Austrian twin beds, a bath and north facing balcony overlooking the Wetterhorn and First mountains.</p>
<p><strong>Standard Single Nova Rooms</strong> are modern and compact at about 14m². They have a single bed (90 x 200 cm), with a shower. </p>
<p><strong>Eiger Standard Twin Rooms </strong>are around 24-26m² and also sleep up to two (single occupancy on request, so please call us to book). These rooms have Austrian twin beds, a bath and south facing balcony overlooking the Eiger and Kleine Scheidegg.</p>
<p><strong>Premium Twin Rooms</strong> are around 24-26m² and sleep up to two. These rooms have Austrian twin beds, either a bath or a shower and a South facing balcony overlooking the Eiger and Kleine Scheidegg.</p>
<p><strong>Room facilities:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Wi-Fi</li>
<li>Cable/satellite TV </li>
<li>Tea and coffee making facilities </li>
<li>Safe </li>
<li>Minibar</li>
<li>Hair dryer</li>
<li>Radio </li>
</ul>
<p> </p>]]></roomsDescription>
